results.name: adagrasib
results.mechanism: Covalently binds the GDP-bound inactive state of KRAS G12C (switch II pocket), locking it inactive and blocking downstream RAF/MEK/ERK signaling.
results.fda_status: Approved for NSCLC and colorectal cancer

results.name: Aspirin
results.mechanism: Binds to switch-II pocket of KRAS, inhibiting G12D/C mutants.

results.name: Trametinib
